{"tid":1002858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"借1.57億港元僅還196萬 香港航空遭銀行入稟追債","createTime":"2019-01-31T08:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T08:51:11.000Z","uid":141151,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4738e14e4531f9e364315c7b0481138944d6cb6f","tid":1002858,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"借1.57億港元僅還196萬 香港航空遭銀行入稟追債<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190131/59206409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F59206409&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6jFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=7c23fe78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F59206409&h=08f19d90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190131/59206409</a><br />\n<br />\n屢傳財困的香港航空再遭債主追討欠款，澳門國際銀行日前入稟高等法院，指港航前年10月借下循環貸款高達2,000萬美元（折合約1.57億港元），但最終逾期不還，銀行現透過法律途徑向港航追討該2,000萬美元本金連利息。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀透露，根據合約，有關貸款原應於去年12月28日償還。惟港航只曾於還款限期屆滿後三度還款，合共僅25萬美金（折合約196萬港元）。澳門國際銀行今年1月，三度向港航發律師信追款不果，最終入稟控告港航。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCA158/19】"},{"pid":"e353522f168b0d76843f744ac0b12bd5c325666c","tid":1002858,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4738e14e4531f9e364315c7b0481138944d6cb6f","tid":1002858,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"借1.57億港元僅還196萬 香港航空遭銀行入稟追債<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190131/59206409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F59206409&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6jFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=7c23fe78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F59206409&h=08f19d90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan